            <note xml:id="n03122401" n="1">
               <name type="person" key="Ladouceur">Ladouceur</name> and <name type="person" key="Bissonette">Bissonette</name> were common French surnames in <name type="place" key="Saint Louis, Mo.">St. Louis</name>; nothing else is known of this man. Osgood (FN), 10 n. 4.</note>
